    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading on the clear coat on the roof and hood. Inside, the upholstery shows significant wear and some staining, but all essential electronics and controls remain functional. Mechanically, the car is dependable for commuting, although it may require some upcoming maintenance for minor leaks and suspension wear. It\u2019s an honest, high-mileage vehicle that gets the job done for anyone looking for affordable transportation.",
